snippet.title: Boogie Ball Game  - App Preview
snippet.description:
The hottest platform game to drop in 2019! Retro game play, funky beats
graffiti, volleyball, endless fun. 

Dodge, bump and block… Test your skills and see how long you last! Download Boogieball now. For adults and kids alike.

Created by hot new indie game developers from the street art community. Czech made.
